Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.41,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.57,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.13,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.27,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:22.62,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:27.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:34.29,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother... when it happened, I was looking at the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at the beautiful sunset reflected on the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweltering heat of the midday was subsiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a cool breeze had begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,34. Ablution
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There's a police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our students must have done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Orihara-kun! Orihara-kun, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Asaka Rei-kun well, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true. The police just notified us about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a case of mistaken identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop lying to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunset was over. I waited until 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I returned home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed that something urgent had come up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that Saint-Juste-sama couldn't make it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"She owes me an outing in the future."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...I told myself that to avoid being too disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I saw Tomoko waiting at the ticket booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I could see clearly that it was indeed Tomoko there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't fathom why she would be meeting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt so strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go... to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama is waiting for you at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, that's all wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Our meeting place is Shiohama station, Lane 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but she couldn't make it and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I see, Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...Saint-Juste-sama sent you to ask me to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But why the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Tomoko... don't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't really understand what Tomoko was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I felt like I was in a strange dream again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go inside. That's the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right. Her room's on the fifth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Tomoko you're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Soup... yes, I should make her some soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? We should make soup before she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For whom? For whom are you going to make soup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who it's for!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know! Surely you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Excuse me please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard... I heard they won't let us take her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... these people think she might have...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't determined that, but we don't have the complete picture yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of policy, we must retain the body for forensic examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can release her body to you by tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Her body... Rei's body... mustn't be touched by a scalpel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If only she left a will...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she was alone at a remote location,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and apparently fell into the path of an oncoming train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are too many unanswered questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing her home, Tomoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me, for any reason at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she someone Nanako knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She was one year older. I hear she was very kind to Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At around 3:15pm today, the body of a student was found near the Shiohama train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was a second year student at the prestigious Seiran High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The body was discovered by a train operator heading in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this point, police have been unable to locate any witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The police have not ruled out suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good. Suicide would not be good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she hold up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably the most shocking event for Nanako in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just at the most delicate and sensitive age, she is met with a close friend's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Her confusion and pain are probably deeper than we can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs to hold up through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She can survive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:11:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Ms. Fukiko Ichinomiya present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss? Miss Fukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A bouquet of roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry to bother you at this hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...we took this order this afternoon but due to our error the delivery was delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To Ichinomiya Fukiko-san from Asaka Rei-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,These flowers are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To your bright future, to your beautiful tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...and foremost, to your love, with all the gratitude I can express.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, just for you... Love, from your one and only sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, just for you, Love, from your one and only sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"With all the gratitude I can express" ...she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you leave this one little letter behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then go off and die by yourself, alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you want me to take that jump myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei... Rei... Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It said so in the morning paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama has passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was taking a lot of drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a lot of pills with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Angel of Death"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I was shocked to hear that it was suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you know, she did fit the profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to get a list of Asaka-san's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Arikura. How is Nanako doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's kept herself in her room since it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't eaten at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry I take her meals, and she does manage to eat about half...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good, then. I just wanted to check how she was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will come by after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... staying at home doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I really was going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that was my intention when I left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But my feet were going another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To the final place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To that final spot where Saint-Juste-sama had said good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She jumped... Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is where she jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do? From now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm overwhelmed with my own emotions right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself can hardly understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a place near here with a particularly beautiful sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Saint-Juste-sama ever speak to you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday... Saint-Juste-sama had planned to take me to a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Planned"? That trip that Rei had planned was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So Rei was passing through here to meet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It was no suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who is committing suicide will not make plans to meet someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Knowing it wasn't suicide makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but it still hurts... the awful reality that she is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't change the fact that we will never hear her voice again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That smile is no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Like yesterday, today was very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon the interruption again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You are acquainted with Misonoo Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Misonoo-san, they had planned an outing yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The overpass was a shortcut, and it seems she took it to save time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have confirmation from Misonoo-san's parents yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Arikura-san provided confirmation that the trip had been planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We will return the body to you this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have concluded that it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an eye witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a delivery person who happened to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was late for his three o'clock appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he saw her fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She tried to reach for the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She tried to grab the flowers that she dropped, and fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And he also said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Asaka-san flew very, very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was terribly unfortunate. A train was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She flew high in the air, like a bird in flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,High...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... my heart has found great strength for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a place with the most beautiful sunset,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...but its location will forever be a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, you gave me these roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Sister, this is your final gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.71,0:23:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You understood that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei... Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:14.08,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:19.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:25.16,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.16,0:24:30.63,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.37,0:24:36.91,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.91,0:24:42.38,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:45.11,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.11,0:24:47.92,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.92,0:24:50.32,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.32,0:24:55.59,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
